com.codename1.rad.nodes

Class PropertyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.rad.models.Attribute<T>
      • com.codename1.rad.nodes.Node<Property>
        • com.codename1.rad.nodes.PropertyNode

  • public class PropertyNode
extends Node<Property>

    A Node for binding a FieldNode to a Property.

    Warning
    		 Avoid binding FieldNodes directly to Propertys. This results in a tight coupling between the view and the model. Prefer to bind to a Tag so that binding can occur dynamically, by binding to a Property that has that Tag at render time.
    Author:
    shannah
    See Also:
